<br>
The Rogue will turn in the components needed to spawn Renux, and back off immediately. The Main Tank will quickly engage with Renux, and everyone else must hold attacks. After approx. 20 seconds, the Main Tank will announce everyone to assist him/her. <br>
<br>
After that, ALL melee's must engage combat and casters nuke. Try to land snare on her also, as she runs quite fast. With 3 groups of people above 50 and 1 tank with Defensive, she should go down quite fast.<br>
